  "texts": [
    "Our theological observations indicate maximal representation of individualistic virtues such as humility, temperance, truthfulness, and wisdom.",
    "Charity, forgiveness, the imago Dei, and stewardship are represented to a lesser extent.",
    "Overall, the theological imperatives, as with the aforementioned social imperatives, demonstrate a distinctly individualistic leaning.",
    "Notably, while the other models show a more pronounced progressive bias, these outputs seem to be more moderate in spirit.",
    "It could be said that these commandments, to some extent, are more suitable as proverbs in that they are, at times, too general and unassuming to be useful."
